{"tid":1373772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要]散水論解決問題","createTime":"2019-07-27T16:15:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T17:05:42.000Z","uid":283781,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bc777fb5e1e2091d1ea756cfb528d99090e17f6a","tid":1373772,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:15:50.000Z","msg":"<strong>(Tldr既睇睇紅字)</strong><br />\n首先經過左200刀手之後<br />\n我相信大部分人都學職左咩叫fact check<br />\n問題黎喇 <br />\n次次都有班人拎住大聲公叫e.g.<br />\n&ldquo;前線話散1930一齊走&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;你地唔走 前面走唔到&rdquo;<br />\n咁究竟大家呢個時候又有冇fact check呢?<br />\n大家要明白 人地在暗我地在明<br />\n佢地可以派鬼入黎扮同路人<br />\n亦會派鬼偷偷局部解封道路<br />\n<br />\n解決方法就黎喇<br />\n大家睇左<span style=\"color: red;\">哨兵tg</span>都相信佢地係<span style=\"color: red;\">reliable source</span><br />\n既然大家話尊重前線<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">前線/會唔會有人 同前線討論<br />\n同哨兵聯絡進退決定<br />\n再由哨兵轉述<br />\n咁大家聽到散水論之後<br />\n可以再fact check左先決定去留</span><br />\n<br />\n但係最好就你地派人落前線 <br />\n始終你地自己個班講個信字 <br />\n最好可以電話溝通到快少少傳達到<br />\n唔知你地本身有冇咁做<br />\n如果有希望你地可以做到前線同後排之間個橋樑<br />\n(Sorry哨兵們知你地辛苦咁講仲要加你地workload)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二 聯絡人既重要性係比人夾個問題<br />\n講返721上環個問題 散水其中一個原因<br />\n係話金鐘比人夾 當日戰線其實太長太散<br />\n大家其實可以去返上環同大隊匯合<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">到時哨兵同聯絡人溝通再同前線討論<br />\n睇下抽唔抽到人去守第二邊又好<br />\n商量進退都好</span><br />\n<br />\n呢個po唔係想拗交<br />\n但係次次都話前線決定<br />\n結果一大堆散水論 無啦啦前線後面冇哂人<br />\n唔係想話揸咪既人 <br />\n但係散水真係次次都係揸咪既講<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">或者揸咪既 講野盡量中立小小<br />\n講下最新既資訊比人聽 唔好加自己感覺<br />\n唔應該講 比人夾緊喇 走呀<br />\n應該講 依家比人夾緊 大家決定走唔走<br />\n我相信出得黎咁大個人 有獨立分析能力</span><br />\n<br />\n最後想拗交既可以過主<br />\n諗唔到其他更好既方法<br />\n有既下面講<br />\n希望大家比少少意見可以幫到個社運"},{"pid":"677e0d76a95c6f8fdac7835f977e6541d4887e22","tid":1373772,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:16:27.000Z","msg":"自推十次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efadcd34424c425f8a2a79eb0fc213909f26858a","tid":1373772,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:16:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"105ea41c09ebd14645e00ea8bbe76dde98c22a4c","tid":1373772,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:16:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd74be7f64fcd30800a63d7453c978a71caf3812","tid":1373772,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:17:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b6048c620fc7b1f5eb4fd5e7a9cfd5a4f215c6c","tid":1373772,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:17:11.000Z","msg":"自動當選選區剩下28個，元朗天水圍區佔13<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1372729\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1372729</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a23f45c12d11d967bc5f079037e590a05a8adb4d","tid":1373772,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:17:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"277bfd3b947b7c9b024623e90bd93c0345717fea","tid":1373772,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:17:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebbb2fa8444a0878b068276ed91088dfd93891a4","tid":1373772,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:17:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f1759318ff50a09e0d5d72eed78675683475cd","tid":1373772,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:18:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59c0c66b4c83cdc60189fc784f5181d8b0e25343","tid":1373772,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:18:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f08eb44c4387b3b9db9f747bbf4610c3e9e620f","tid":1373772,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:18:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79028a0069dfde8f86ea3f6f196903ed2957ae44","tid":1373772,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:18:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828401a89ef39c5651adaec7ddc96b4a35a8c6f0","tid":1373772,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:19:13.000Z","msg":"勇武決定左要留，已經做好比攻擊準備，<br />\n真正留喺現場嘅勇武兄弟，<br />\n係唔會怪自已人離開，<br />\n即使離開現場，<br />\n和理非心中都會支持留守兄弟決定，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">留下：支持；離開：專重</span></span><br />\n有班3毛扮勇武屌自己人散水，<br />\n和理非唔好被影響到<br />\n<br />\n勇武其實已經有左付死嘅決心，<br />\n死都唔怕，點會怕比人拉同比人打，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武在乎嘅係用自己嘅生命去揭露政權嘅邪惡，</span></span><br />\n我地應該給予最大專重同支持，<br />\n留低嘅人就盡量留到最後，<br />\n直至政府宣布特赦呢班義士為止<br />\n<br />\n【散水】有份叫人730走嘅入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1373646\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1373646</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e7c68a02ca4b3521eff888fd21d2e9ac95bb0f64","tid":1373772,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:20:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3343dec39f731202853dd38a84a42b4cceede34b","tid":1373772,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7c68a02ca4b3521eff888fd21d2e9ac95bb0f64","tid":1373772,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:20:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:21:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"764d9f0c0cd1462ceff4cfb310c0082888d1f2cc","tid":1373772,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:24:05.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"639471da23a13c368977e9db6b8274f54f961c4f","tid":1373772,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:26:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/n